b. Equipment specially designed for the inspection or testing of semiconductor devices, integrated circuits and «electronic assemblies», as follows, and systems incorporating or having the characteristics of such equipment:Note:X.B.I.002.b also controls equipment used or modified for use in the inspection or testing of other devices, such as imaging devices, electro-optical devices, acoustic-wave devices.
