X.B.VII.002 Specially designed «equipment», tooling or fixtures for manufacturing or measuring gas turbine blades, vanes or tip shroud castings, as follows:
Automated equipment using non-mechanical methods for measuring airfoil wall hickness;
Tooling, fixtures or measuring equipment for the «laser», water jet or ECM/EDM hole drilling processes controlled by 9E003.c1;
Ceramic core leaching equipment;
